### 测试4：同步数据到云端（POST）
### 把下面的 Bearer 后面替换成你登录得到的 token
### ==============================
POST http://localhost:3001/api/sync
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6MSwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJ0ZXN0dXNlciIsImlhdCI6MTc3NTk4OTM5MywiZXhwIjoxNzc2NTk0MTkzfQ.P7uyhem1H22WjCWwFqR3-7jlUWhxAW3fnLaClLGYGTc

{
  "recordId": "test001",
  "target": "测试闪光精灵",
  "captures": [1,2,3],
  "quickButtons": [1,2]
}

